MINISTER MOHAMMAD ZARIF CALLED

03:06.200 --> 03:07.500
FOR ARAB UNITY AND SAID NO

03:07.500 --> 03:08.367
COUNTRY CAN SOLVE REGIONAL

03:08.367 --> 03:09.167
PROBLEMS WITHOUT THE HELP OF

03:09.167 --> 03:10.100
OTHERS.

