>> TERRORISM IN AFRICA IS A

04:34.467 --> 04:36.533
DIRECT THREAT, NOT TO U.S.

04:36.533 --> 04:40.767
SECURITY, BUT TO U.S. INTERESTS.

04:40.767 --> 04:46.100
A FUNDAMENTAL U.S. INTEREST IN

04:46.100 --> 04:48.033
AFRICA IS THERE BE CONTINUED

04:48.033 --> 04:50.333
PROGRESS TOWARDS DEMOCRACY,

04:50.333 --> 04:54.600
TOWARDS DEVELOPMENT TOWARDS

04:54.600 --> 04:56.700
STABILITY.

