>> LET'S LOOK AT THE ECONOMIC

05:07.867 --> 05:08.967
IMPACT AS WELL.

05:08.967 --> 05:10.767
THERE SEEMS TO BE ALMOST A RACE

05:10.767 --> 05:14.133
HERE TO PERHAPS COUNTER THE

05:14.133 --> 05:15.600
INFLUENCE THAT CHINA HAS ALREADY

05:15.600 --> 05:18.567
IN AFRICA AS A TRADING PARTNER

05:18.567 --> 05:22.533
AS A COUNTRY THAT IS MAKING

05:22.533 --> 05:23.400
SIGNIFICANT INVESTMENTS THERE.

05:23.400 --> 05:28.000
>> MY VIEW THAT THAT CAN BE

05:28.000 --> 05:29.000
OVEREMPHASIZED.

