THE REAL INTEREST IS THAT

05:35.300 --> 05:37.033
CHINESE ECONOMIC INTERESTS IN

05:37.033 --> 05:38.500
AFRICA BE RESPONSIBLE.

05:38.500 --> 05:40.200
AND THAT PARTICULAR IN PEACE AND

05:40.200 --> 05:41.567
SECURITY QUESTIONS, THAT CHINA

05:41.567 --> 05:44.700
PLAY A ROLE, COMMENSURATE WITH

05:44.700 --> 05:46.833
ITS ECONOMIC POSITION IN

05:46.833 --> 05:48.767
PARTICULARLY EAST AFRICA.

