LITTLE INTRAAFRICAN TRADE.

06:25.267 --> 06:27.267
SO THERE IS A LOT OF DEVELOPMENT

06:27.267 --> 06:31.900
TO BE DONE.

06:31.900 --> 06:38.267
>> CLINTON AND BUSH AS WELL,

06:38.267 --> 06:40.167
PEPFAR, EMERGENCY AIDS RELIEF.

