>> THERE WAS INDEED.

06:47.433 --> 06:50.900
ALSO VERY IMPORTANT U.S.

06:50.900 --> 06:54.233
INITIATIVE THAT'S BEEN

06:54.233 --> 07:00.667
OVERLOOKED IS MALARIA.

