SIMPLE PROGRAMS SUCH AS

07:02.100 --> 07:03.600
PROVIDING BED NETS FOR PEOPLE,

07:03.600 --> 07:10.833
CAN GREATLY REDUCE THE MORTALITY

07:10.833 --> 07:12.533
RATES ESPECIALLY FOR CHILDREN.

07:12.533 --> 07:14.300
>> PRESIDENT OBAMA LEAVING

07:14.300 --> 07:19.833
BEHIND A DIFFERENT BECAUSE OF

07:19.833 --> 07:21.100
HIS BACKGROUND?

