IS AN AFRICAN AMERICAN, THAT IS

07:44.533 --> 07:45.967
OF PARTICULAR INTEREST AND

07:45.967 --> 07:47.700
INDEED EVEN PRIDE STRAIGHT

07:47.700 --> 07:49.933
ACROSS THE AFRICAN CONTINENT.

07:49.933 --> 07:51.433
SO YES, BOTH IN THE UNITED

07:51.433 --> 07:53.067
STATES BUT ALSO IN AFRICA.

07:53.067 --> 07:55.467
>> ALL RIGHT JOHN CAMPBELL,

