SHORE, AND PAY FOR EXTRA FUEL TO

10:39.233 --> 10:41.133
GET THEM THERE.

10:41.133 --> 10:42.833
SOMETIMES THESE UNTRAINED

10:42.833 --> 10:44.500
FISHERMAN RISK THEIR OWN LIVES

10:44.500 --> 10:46.133
PULLING PEOPLE OUT OF THE WATER,

10:46.133 --> 10:47.400
AND SPEND ALL NIGHT WAITING FOR

10:47.400 --> 10:48.333
HELP FROM THE TUNISIAN COAST

10:48.333 --> 10:53.867
GUARD.

10:53.867 --> 10:54.767
>> (translated): IT'S A

10:54.767 --> 10:56.133
POWERFUL FEELING TO SEE SOMEONE

10:56.133 --> 10:57.233
HELPLESS, HUNGRY AND BEING

10:57.233 --> 10:58.867
BURNED BY THE SUN.

10:58.867 --> 11:00.300
IT'S VERY HARD, YOU ARE IN FRONT

11:00.300 --> 11:01.133
OF SOMEONE WHO IS CALLING FOR

11:01.133 --> 11:06.767
HELP.

11:06.767 --> 11:08.333
>> Reporter: MONGI SLIM IS THE

11:08.333 --> 11:10.300
HEAD OF THE ZARZIS OFFICE OF THE

11:10.300 --> 11:11.867
TUNISIAN RED CRESCENT; THE RED

11:11.867 --> 11:14.033
CROSS IN MUSLIM COUNTRIES.

11:14.033 --> 11:16.367
AT THE LOCAL FISHING ASSOCIATION

11:16.367 --> 11:17.767
HE COORDINATES RESCUES... IN

11:17.767 --> 11:19.033
ZARZIS AND OTHER NEARBY PORT

11:19.033 --> 11:22.067
CITIES LIKE BEN GARDANE.

11:22.067 --> 11:23.833
>> THOSE PEOPLE ARE FIGHTING,

11:23.833 --> 11:27.733
EACH ONE WANTS TO GO.

11:27.733 --> 11:28.600
>> Reporter: AND I SEE SOME

11:28.600 --> 11:29.533
PICTURES HERE OF THE BODIES

11:29.533 --> 11:31.133
WASHED UP?

11:31.133 --> 11:32.700
>> YES, THIS, THIS HERE IS IN

11:32.700 --> 11:34.133
BEN GARDANE.

11:34.133 --> 11:37.933
THESE ARE SYRIAN PEOPLE.

11:37.933 --> 11:39.033
HERE IS IN IL KITIF, THE PORT OF

11:39.033 --> 11:41.933
BEN GARDANE.

11:41.933 --> 11:43.700
WE RECEIVED THIS DAY 54 BODIES

11:43.700 --> 11:46.333
FROM SYRIA.

11:46.333 --> 11:48.533
>> Reporter: PHOTO AFTER PHOTO

11:48.533 --> 11:50.433
SHOWS OVERCROWDED BOATS-- MEN

11:50.433 --> 11:51.933
AND WOMEN FIGHTING TO STAY

11:51.933 --> 11:53.300
ALIVE-- AND MIGRANTS DESPERATELY

11:53.300 --> 11:55.167
FLAGGING SHIPS FOR HELP.

11:55.167 --> 11:57.000
WHEN THE FISHERMEN FIND THE

11:57.000 --> 11:58.533
SINKING BOATS, IF THEY ARE CLOSE

11:58.533 --> 12:00.200
ENOUGH TO EUROPEAN WATERS, THEY

12:00.200 --> 12:01.767
CALL THE ITALIAN AUTHORITIES,

12:01.767 --> 12:02.767
BUT SOMETIMES, THE ITALIANS

12:02.767 --> 12:04.100
DON'T SHOW UP.

12:04.100 --> 12:05.667
>> HE HAD TO RESCUE THEM

12:05.667 --> 12:06.933
HIMSELF, BECAUSE NOBODY COME.

12:06.933 --> 12:09.100
AND HE WAITS A LONG TIME AND

12:09.100 --> 12:11.933
NOBODY COME, AND PEOPLE ARE

12:11.933 --> 12:13.433
CRYING IN THE SEA, AND HE MUST

12:13.433 --> 12:16.433
HELP THEM.

12:16.433 --> 12:18.033
>> Reporter: THE LUCKY ONES WHO

12:18.033 --> 12:19.367
MAKE IT TO ZARZIS ALIVE GET HELP

12:19.367 --> 12:21.833
FROM THE RED CRESCENT.

12:21.833 --> 12:23.800
MONGI EARNS HIS LIVING AS A

12:23.800 --> 12:25.567
PHARMACIST, AND HAS MADE IT HIS

12:25.567 --> 12:27.100
VOLUNTEER MISSION TO PROVIDE THE

12:27.100 --> 12:28.133
MIGRANTS WITH SHELTER, FOOD, AND

12:28.133 --> 12:29.833
SUPPORT TO SURVIVE.

12:29.833 --> 12:30.700
CAN YOU TELL ME HOW MANY PEOPLE

12:30.700 --> 12:33.133
LIVE HERE?

12:33.133 --> 12:35.033
>> IN THIS HOUSE, WE HAVE FOUR.

12:35.033 --> 12:36.467
>> Reporter: 18-YEAR-OLD TUBA--

12:36.467 --> 12:37.500
ON THE RIGHT-- IS FROM SENEGAL.

12:37.500 --> 12:38.733
HOW DID YOU END UP HERE IN

12:38.733 --> 12:42.300
TUNISIA?

12:42.300 --> 12:43.433
>> (translated): WE WERE

12:43.433 --> 12:44.700
TRYING TO GO ITALY.

12:44.700 --> 12:45.900
WE LEFT ZWARA TO GO TO

12:45.900 --> 12:47.133
LAMPEDUSA.

12:47.133 --> 12:48.233
>> Reporter: DO YOU REMEMBER THE

12:48.233 --> 12:49.300
DAY THAT YOU WERE RESCUED?

12:49.300 --> 12:54.000
WHAT HAPPENED?

12:54.000 --> 12:55.033
>> (translated): WE SAW LOTS

12:55.033 --> 12:56.167
OF BOATS.

12:56.167 --> 12:57.433
WE WERE TRYING TO CALL THEM, BUT

12:57.433 --> 12:59.733
THEY DIDN'T RESPOND.

12:59.733 --> 13:01.000
>> Reporter: THERE ARE NOW

13:01.000 --> 13:02.467
SEVERAL HUNDRED MIGRANTS AND

13:02.467 --> 13:03.633
REFUGEES FROM AFRICA AND THE

13:03.633 --> 13:04.500
MIDDLE EAST LIVING IN THE AREA

13:04.500 --> 13:06.267
AROUND ZARZIS.

13:06.267 --> 13:07.800
MANY FLED WAR, POVERTY, OR

13:07.800 --> 13:08.800
PERSECUTION IN THEIR HOME

13:08.800 --> 13:11.200
COUNTRIES.

13:11.200 --> 13:12.800
SOME STAY ONLY A FEW WEEKS,

13:12.800 --> 13:14.600
BEFORE WALKING 80 MILES ACROSS

13:14.600 --> 13:15.933
THE BORDER TO LIBYA, TO BOARD

13:15.933 --> 13:17.033
BOATS BOUND FOR EUROPE.

13:17.033 --> 13:19.500
ONE MORE TIME.

13:19.500 --> 13:21.633
OUSMAN KEBBEH IS FROM GAMBIA.

13:21.633 --> 13:23.167
HE JOURNEYED BY SEA TO EUROPE

13:23.167 --> 13:25.000
THREE TIMES.

13:25.000 --> 13:26.400
THE FIRST TWO TIMES, HE DIDN'T

13:26.400 --> 13:27.933
GET FAR-- HE WAS RESCUED AND

13:27.933 --> 13:30.967
RETURNED TO LIBYA.

13:30.967 --> 13:32.133
DURING HIS FINAL ATTEMPT, HE WAS

13:32.133 --> 13:35.567
SAVED BY TUNISIAN FISHERMEN.

13:35.567 --> 13:37.233
>> WE JUST WAITING FOR OUR

13:37.233 --> 13:39.533
DEATHS, NO OPTIONS.

13:39.533 --> 13:41.700
YOU JUST INSIDE THE BOAT WAITING

13:41.700 --> 13:44.967
FOR OUR TIME TO DIE.

13:44.967 --> 13:46.800
>> Reporter: THE FISHERMEN SENT

13:46.800 --> 13:48.200
US THIS CELL PHONE FOOTAGE THAT

13:48.200 --> 13:50.033
SHOWS OUSMAN'S RESCUE.

13:50.033 --> 13:51.767
HE WAS ONBOARD A PLASTIC RAFT,

13:51.767 --> 13:53.333
CRAMMED WITH 90 OTHER PEOPLE,

13:53.333 --> 13:55.233
HEADING TO ITALY.

13:55.233 --> 13:56.767
EVENTUALLY, THE BOAT SPRUNG A

13:56.767 --> 13:57.867
LEAK AND SLOWLY BEGAN TO FILL

13:57.867 --> 14:06.367
WITH WATER.

14:06.367 --> 14:07.600
>> THE WATER IS ENTERING INSIDE,

14:07.600 --> 14:08.433
AND THE WAVES IS COMING AGAIN,

14:08.433 --> 14:09.267
THE WATER IS COMING UP.

14:09.267 --> 14:10.133
SO THE WATER IS COMING DIFFERENT

14:10.133 --> 14:10.967
DIRECTIONS.

14:10.967 --> 14:11.833
YOU DON'T KNOW WHERE EXACTLY

14:11.833 --> 14:12.833
WATER IS ENTERING THE BOAT.

14:12.833 --> 14:13.767
SO IT'S A TERRIBLE SITUATION.

14:13.767 --> 14:15.033
SOME PEOPLE ARE VOMITING, SOME

14:15.033 --> 14:16.900
PEOPLE ARE CRYING, SOME PEOPLE

14:16.900 --> 14:18.767
ARE FIGHTING BECAUSE YOU BECOME

14:18.767 --> 14:21.300
CRAZY ON THE SEA.

14:21.300 --> 14:23.800
YOU BECOME DIFFERENT MAN.

14:23.800 --> 14:25.200
SO I WAS JUST THINKING TWO

14:25.200 --> 14:26.300
THINGS, THAT I WILL SURVIVE, OR

14:26.300 --> 14:27.967
I WILL DIE.

14:27.967 --> 14:30.567
THIS IS IT.

14:30.567 --> 14:32.467
>> Reporter: LIKE MOST MIGRANTS,

14:32.467 --> 14:34.033
OUSMAN HAD PUT HIS FATE IN THE

14:34.033 --> 14:35.500
HANDS OF HUMAN SMUGGLERS WHO

14:35.500 --> 14:36.767
TYPICALLY LEAVE THE MIGRANTS TO

14:36.767 --> 14:38.700
DRIVE THE BOATS THEMSELVES.

14:38.700 --> 14:40.767
THE JOURNEY CAN TAKE MORE THAN

14:40.767 --> 14:42.467
24 HOURS, THEY HAVE FEW TOOLS TO

14:42.467 --> 14:44.133
NAVIGATE, SOMETIMES RELYING ON

14:44.133 --> 14:45.067
JUST A COMPASS TO FIND THEIR WAY

14:45.067 --> 14:47.300
TO EUROPE.

14:47.300 --> 14:49.133
IN ZARZIS IT IS COMMON KNOWLEDGE

14:49.133 --> 14:50.733
THAT ONE OF THE WAYS THAT

14:50.733 --> 14:52.467
SMUGGLERS LURE MIGRANTS IS BY

14:52.467 --> 14:54.767
ADVERTISING ON SOCIAL MEDIA WITH

14:54.767 --> 14:56.500
POSTS LIKE THESE: FEATURING

14:56.500 --> 14:58.333
PICTURES OF CRUISE SHIPS, THEY

14:58.333 --> 15:00.133
PROMISE A SAFE JOURNEY, WITH

15:00.133 --> 15:02.033
CHILDREN RIDING FREE.

15:02.033 --> 15:04.200
THIS POST, WHICH WAS RECENTLY

15:04.200 --> 15:06.767
TAKEN DOWN, LISTS THE PRICE PER

15:06.767 --> 15:08.200
ADULT: $1,000 TO BE FERRIED FROM

15:08.200 --> 15:11.433
LIBYA TO ITALY.

15:11.433 --> 15:13.100
OUSMAN IS ONE OF THOUSANDS OF

15:13.100 --> 15:14.667
MIGRANTS WHO HAVE FLOCKED TO THE

15:14.667 --> 15:16.433
WAR TORN COUNTRY BASED ON THE

15:16.433 --> 15:18.633
PROMISE OF MAKING IT TO EUROPE.

15:18.633 --> 15:20.267
BUT ONCE THEY ARRIVE IN LIBYA,

15:20.267 --> 15:21.867
THEY ARE CAUGHT IN VIOLENCE AND

15:21.867 --> 15:23.400
LAWLESSNESS, AND NO CHOICE BUT

15:23.400 --> 15:24.333
TO RISK THEIR LIVES ON THE

15:24.333 --> 15:26.867
MEDITERRANEAN.

15:26.867 --> 15:28.833
>> YOU CANNOT LIVE IN LIBYA.

15:28.833 --> 15:30.200
PEOPLE IN LIBYA, THEY JUST KEEP

15:30.200 --> 15:31.700
ON HARASSING BLACK PEOPLE, KEEP

15:31.700 --> 15:32.533
ON BEATING THEM, KEEP ON LOCK

15:32.533 --> 15:33.567
THEM.

15:33.567 --> 15:34.600
SOME OF THEM KIDNAP YOU IN YOUR

15:34.600 --> 15:36.100
HOUSES, LOCK YOU.

15:36.100 --> 15:39.033
YOU HAVE TO PAY MONEY FOR THEM

15:39.033 --> 15:40.300
OTHERWISE THEY'LL KILL.

15:40.300 --> 15:41.267
SO THE ONLY THING YOU HAVE TO

15:41.267 --> 15:42.133
GO, YOU HAVE TO CROSS TO ITALY.

15:42.133 --> 15:42.933
THIS IS A PROBLEM.

15:42.933 --> 15:44.167
LIBYAN SITUATION IS WORSE,

15:44.167 --> 15:45.033
BECAUSE THERE IS NO GOVERNMENT,

15:45.033 --> 15:49.100
NOBODY IS CONTROL.

15:49.100 --> 15:50.367
>> Reporter: LAST YEAR, THE

15:50.367 --> 15:51.467
TUNISIAN RED CRESCENT TOOK IN

15:51.467 --> 15:53.333
700 MIGRANTS, AND SO FAR THIS

15:53.333 --> 15:54.200
YEAR THE NUMBER HAS ALREADY

15:54.200 --> 15:56.033
DOUBLED.

15:56.033 --> 15:57.900
MONGI SLIM IS WORRIED ABOUT HOW

15:57.900 --> 15:59.433
TO HANDLE THE GROWING NUMBER OF

15:59.433 --> 16:00.533
MIGRANTS ENDING UP IN THE PORT

16:00.533 --> 16:03.133
CITY OF ZARZIS.

16:03.133 --> 16:04.767
>> NOBODY NOW IS HELPING ENOUGH

16:04.767 --> 16:07.967
THIS PEOPLE.

16:07.967 --> 16:09.200
OUR GOVERNMENT ALSO, WE DON'T

16:09.200 --> 16:10.500
HAVE ANY SHELTER HERE TO THIS

16:10.500 --> 16:11.967
PEOPLE.

16:11.967 --> 16:13.000
WHEN THEY ARRIVE, WE HAVE A BIG

16:13.000 --> 16:24.333
PROBLEM TO RESOLVE THE SHELTER.

16:24.333 --> 16:25.433
>> Reporter: THE DREAM IS TO

16:25.433 --> 16:26.233
MAKE A BETTER LIFE THAN THEY

16:26.233 --> 16:30.667
HAVE IN THERE COUNTRY.

16:30.667 --> 16:31.933
THEIR COUNTRY, THEY WANT TO

16:31.933 --> 16:33.367
SUPPORT THEIR FAMILY.

16:33.367 --> 16:34.733
BUT I THINK THAT THEY CANNOT GET

16:34.733 --> 16:37.433
IT.

16:37.433 --> 16:38.567
>> THE FISHERMAN SAY THEY WILL

16:38.567 --> 16:44.967
CONTINUE RESCUING MIGRANTS.

16:44.967 --> 16:45.833
>> (translated): IT IS RISKY

16:45.833 --> 16:46.700
FOR US, BECAUSE THERE'S

16:46.700 --> 16:47.567
BACTERIA, DISEASE.

16:47.567 --> 16:48.700
AND PEOPLE ARE AFRAID.

16:48.700 --> 16:49.700
BUT IT IS A HUMANITARIAN DUTY,

16:49.700 --> 16:58.200
AND WE DO IT WILLINGLY.

16:58.200 --> 17:00.867
>> THEY ARE GOOD PEOPLE, THEY

17:00.867 --> 17:01.933
LOVE THE SEA, SO THEY CAN'T JUST

17:01.933 --> 17:03.267
SEE PEOPLE DIE AND LEAVE THEM

17:03.267 --> 17:06.600
LIKE THAT.

17:06.600 --> 17:08.767
THEY SAVE MANY LIVES IN THE SEA.

17:08.767 --> 17:11.100
NOT ONLY US, BUT MANY PEOPLE.

17:11.100 --> 17:11.933
AND I HOPE THEY ARE STILL DOING

17:11.933 --> 17:25.000
IT.

17:25.000 --> 17:26.400
>> Sreenivasan: PHOTOGRAPHS ARE

17:26.400 --> 17:27.700
A FUNDAMENTAL PART OF HOW WE

17:27.700 --> 17:29.333
DOCUMENT CURRENT EVENTS.

17:29.333 --> 17:31.167
BUT IN THE DIGITAL AGE, THE

17:31.167 --> 17:32.700
TOOLS TO EDIT AND DOCTOR PHOTOS

17:32.700 --> 17:33.900
ARE ACCESSIBLE TO ANYONE WITH A

17:33.900 --> 17:35.933
COMPUTER OR SMARTPHONE.

17:35.933 --> 17:37.800
AN EXHIBIT IN NEW YORK EXPLORES

17:37.800 --> 17:39.567
PROMINENT CASES OF IMAGES

17:39.567 --> 17:41.767
ALTERED BY JOURNALISTS AND ASKS:

17:41.767 --> 17:43.300
IF SEEING IS BELIEVING, HOW

17:43.300 --> 17:44.433
OFTEN ARE YOU, THE VIEWER OR

17:44.433 --> 17:46.100
READER, BEING MISLED?

17:46.100 --> 17:46.933
THE NEWSHOUR'S SASKIA DE MELKER

17:46.933 --> 17:49.433
REPORTS.

17:49.433 --> 17:50.367
>> Reporter: WHEN YOU DON'T LIKE

17:50.367 --> 17:51.400
THOSE PEOPLE OR OBJECTS IN THE

17:51.400 --> 17:52.300
BACKGROUND, YOU JUST REMOVE

17:52.300 --> 17:53.833
THEM.

17:53.833 --> 17:55.533
USING A FILTER, AFTER THE SNAP,

17:55.533 --> 17:57.033
TO MAKE A REGULAR PHOTO LOOK

17:57.033 --> 17:57.833
VINTAGE, IS AS EASY AS A MOUSE

17:57.833 --> 17:59.400
CLICK.

17:59.400 --> 18:01.100
SO IS REMOVING A LIGHT POST THAT

18:01.100 --> 18:02.600
SEEMS TO BE SHOOTING OUT OF

18:02.600 --> 18:03.400
SOMEONE'S HEAD BY USING

18:03.400 --> 18:04.600
PHOTOSHOP.

18:04.600 --> 18:06.100
BUT IN THE WORLD OF

18:06.100 --> 18:07.133
PHOTOJOURNALISM, THESE

18:07.133 --> 18:07.967
ALTERATIONS ARE THE SUBJECT OF

18:07.967 --> 18:09.767
INTENSE DEBATE.

18:09.767 --> 18:10.833
AND USING PHOTOSHOP CAN LAND YOU

18:10.833 --> 18:12.800
IN HOT WATER.

18:12.800 --> 18:14.767
LIKE IT DID FOR "THE ECONOMIST"

18:14.767 --> 18:16.100
WHEN IT REMOVED PEOPLE FROM THIS

18:16.100 --> 18:18.300
BEACH PHOTO OF PRESIDENT OBAMA.

18:18.300 --> 18:20.067
OR FOR AN ORTHODOX ISRAELI

18:20.067 --> 18:21.367
NEWSPAPER WHEN IT CUT OUT THE

18:21.367 --> 18:22.967
FEMALE LEADERS IN THIS PHOTO.

18:22.967 --> 18:23.800
>> PEOPLE DO THAT ALL THE TIME

18:23.800 --> 18:24.600
ON THEIR FACEBOOK PAGE.

18:24.600 --> 18:25.767
THAT'S FINE.

18:25.767 --> 18:26.800
WE'RE THE PROFESSIONALS.

18:26.800 --> 18:27.833
WE HAVE TO MAINTAIN STANDARDS

18:27.833 --> 18:29.033
AND ETHICS.

18:29.033 --> 18:30.333
WE HAVE TO MAKE SURE THAT THESE

18:30.333 --> 18:31.200
PHOTOS ARE AN ACCURATE

18:31.200 --> 18:32.333
REPRESENTATION.

18:32.333 --> 18:33.600
>> Reporter: PHOTOGRAPHER

18:33.600 --> 18:34.733
MICHAEL KAMBER HAS COVERED

18:34.733 --> 18:35.700
CONFLICTS AROUND THE WORLD FOR

18:35.700 --> 18:37.700
THE "NEW YORK TIMES."

18:37.700 --> 18:39.200
HIS LATEST PROJECT, THOUGH, IS

18:39.200 --> 18:41.033
CURATING AN EXHIBITION AT THE

18:41.033 --> 18:43.000
BRONX DOCUMENTARY CENTER CALLED"

18:43.000 --> 18:44.533
ALTERED IMAGES," WHICH EXPLORES

18:44.533 --> 18:45.567
NEWS AND DOCUMENTARY PHOTOS THAT

18:45.567 --> 18:47.500
HAVE BEEN MANIPULATED.

18:47.500 --> 18:50.300
>> THE MORE WE LOOKED, THE MORE

18:50.300 --> 18:51.700
WE FOUND, ESPECIALLY LATELY,

18:51.700 --> 18:53.133
ESPECIALLY IN THE DIGITAL AGE.

18:53.133 --> 18:54.033
IT WAS ACTUALLY HARD TO BRING IT

18:54.033 --> 18:55.700
DOWN TO THESE 40 PHOTOS.

18:55.700 --> 18:57.067
>> Reporter: THE EXHIBIT SPANS

18:57.067 --> 18:58.867
PHOTOJOURNALISM HISTORY AND

18:58.867 --> 19:00.800
INCLUDES EXAMPLES OF STAGING:

19:00.800 --> 19:02.600
DIRECTING SUBJECTS LIKE THE BOY

19:02.600 --> 19:04.167
IN THIS IMAGE.

19:04.167 --> 19:05.867
OR MISLEADING CAPTIONS: THIS MAN

19:05.867 --> 19:09.033
WAS NOT A SNIPER.

19:09.033 --> 19:11.667
AND YES, PHOTOSHOPPING: JOHN

19:11.667 --> 19:12.567
KERRY WAS NEVER AT THIS ANTI-

19:12.567 --> 19:14.800
VIETNAM RALLY WITH JANE FONDA.

19:14.800 --> 19:16.500
ONE OF THE FIRST CASES OF

19:16.500 --> 19:18.600
CONTROVERSIAL DIGITAL PHOTO

19:18.600 --> 19:19.667
MANIPULATION OCCURRED IN 1982

19:19.667 --> 19:20.533
WITH THE GREAT PYRAMIDS OF

19:20.533 --> 19:22.067
EGYPT.

19:22.067 --> 19:23.600
>> NATIONAL GEOGRAPHIC TOOK A

19:23.600 --> 19:24.967
HORIZONTAL PHOTO AND WANTED TO

19:24.967 --> 19:26.533
PUT IT ON A VERTICAL COVER.

19:26.533 --> 19:27.600
AND THEY MOVED THE PYRAMIDS

19:27.600 --> 19:28.867
CLOSER TOGETHER.

19:28.867 --> 19:29.700
THAT WAS SOMETHING THAT REALLY

19:29.700 --> 19:31.833
GOT PEOPLE'S ATTENTION.

19:31.833 --> 19:33.700
ANOTHER REALLY EGREGIOUS EXAMPLE

19:33.700 --> 19:36.767
OF MANIPULATION IS THE LOS

19:36.767 --> 19:38.700
ANGELES TIMES PHOTO FROM 2003,

19:38.700 --> 19:39.533
WHERE A PHOTOGRAPHER TOOK TWO

19:39.533 --> 19:41.533
PHOTOS.

19:41.533 --> 19:43.533
THEY WERE BOTH QUITE DRAMATIC.

19:43.533 --> 19:45.567
THERE WAS A BRITISH SOLDIER IN

19:45.567 --> 19:46.367
THE PHOTO AND THERE WAS AN IRAQI

19:46.367 --> 19:49.233
CIVILIAN.

19:49.233 --> 19:50.167
IN ONE PHOTO HE LIKED THE WAY

19:50.167 --> 19:51.333
THE SOLDIER LOOKED.

19:51.333 --> 19:52.533
AND IN THE OTHER PHOTO HE LIKED

19:52.533 --> 19:54.033
THE WAY THE CIVILIAN LOOKED.

19:54.033 --> 19:55.500
SO HE DECIDED TO JUST COMBINE

19:55.500 --> 19:57.333
THE TWO PHOTOS IN PHOTOSHOP.

19:57.333 --> 19:58.233
AND IT WAS ACTUALLY PRINTED ALL

19:58.233 --> 19:59.333
OVER THE WORLD.

19:59.333 --> 20:00.600
>> Reporter: WHEN THE

20:00.600 --> 20:02.267
INCONSISTENCIES WERE NOTICED,

20:02.267 --> 20:05.000
THE PHOTOGRAPHER LOST HIS JOB.

20:05.000 --> 20:06.200
PHOTO MANIPULATION IS AS OLD AS

20:06.200 --> 20:08.000
PHOTOGRAPHY ITSELF.

20:08.000 --> 20:08.900
TAKE THIS PHOTO OF PRESIDENT

20:08.900 --> 20:10.600
LINCOLN.

20:10.600 --> 20:12.233
IT'S ACTUALLY LINCOLN'S HEAD ON

20:12.233 --> 20:14.233
SENATOR JOHN CALHOUN'S BODY.

20:14.233 --> 20:15.767
OR THIS PORTRAIT OF GENERAL

20:15.767 --> 20:17.867
ULYSSES GRANT.

20:17.867 --> 20:19.200
IT LAYERS THREE SEPARATE IMAGES

20:19.200 --> 20:20.100
FROM DIFFERENT TIMES AND

20:20.100 --> 20:21.967
LOCATIONS.

20:21.967 --> 20:23.400
EVEN BEFORE PHOTOGRAPHY WENT

20:23.400 --> 20:24.233
DIGITAL, THE MEDIA ALTERED

20:24.233 --> 20:26.033
PHOTOS.

20:26.033 --> 20:27.700
IN THIS FAMOUS IMAGE OF THE KENT

20:27.700 --> 20:29.433
STATE MASSACRE, THE FENCE BEHIND

20:29.433 --> 20:30.500
THE GRIEVING TEENAGE GIRL WAS

